dct_description_sm: Relief shown by contours. "Administrative boundaries revised 1948". Map shows international, provincial and district boundaries, radioelectric stations. Includes aeronautical information. Includes index to Gazetteer Reference, and a diagram showing magnetic variation 1939. In lower left margin: "Z373" Original map is filed in the Map/Geospatial Center, a map reproduction is attached to volume. Map shows international, provincial and district boundaries, radioelectric stations.
dct_publisher_sm: Dar-es-Salaam : Survey Division, Dept., Lands & Mines Tanganyika Territory, 1948.
